PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777968371
OL,3,CMan, 91, to cycle over 500 miles to
OL,4,Craise money for youth zone
OL,6,FA 91-year-old man is set to take on a
OL,7,Fcycle of over 500 miles to raise money
OL,8,Ffor a youth zone.
OL,10,FTony Newton will set off on the 523
OL,11,Fmile challenge on Sunday 10 May,
OL,12,Fmarking his fourth challenge for
OL,13,FInspire Youth Zone in Chorley.
OL,15,FHe has organised the route himself,
OL,16,Fstarting in Chorley, heading towards
OL,17,FDerbyshire, accompanied by family and
OL,18,Ffriends for the first section of the
OL,19,Ftrip.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777968371
OL,3,CMan, 91, to cycle over 500 miles to
OL,4,Craise money for youth zone
OL,6,FTony will then be on his own as he
OL,7,Fheads off to the Pennines and
OL,8,FBrotherton, crossing Yorkshire until
OL,9,Fhe reaches the coast at Bridlington.
OL,11,FFrom there he will head north through
OL,12,FScarborough and Whitby up to Newcastle
OL,13,Fand then across the Hadrian's Wall
OL,14,Fcoast to coast cycleway to Carlisle,
OL,15,Freturning South through Penrith, Shap,
OL,16,FLancaster and back to Heskin around 22
OL,17,FMay.
OL,19,FThe route has a total climb of 30,748
OL,20,Ffeet.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777968371
OL,3,CMan, 91, to cycle over 500 miles to
OL,4,Craise money for youth zone
OL,6,FTony said: 'I've been going on a long,
OL,7,Fsolitary trek every year for about 15
OL,8,Fyears. Four years ago, my
OL,9,Fgranddaughter caught me and said
OL,10,F'you're wasting your time here, why
OL,11,Faren't you sponsoring yourself?' So
OL,12,Fthat's how it started four years ago."
OL,14,FHis first challenge saw him cycle
OL,15,Faround 400 miles, from Chorley to
OL,16,FInverness, before cycling around the
OL,17,FIsle of Skye the year after.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777968371
OL,3,CMan, 91, to cycle over 500 miles to
OL,4,Craise money for youth zone
OL,6,FLast year, Tony cycled from the
OL,7,FEnglish Channel to the Mediterranean,
OL,8,Fraising a total of #22,652 for the
OL,9,FInspire Youth Zone so far.
OL,11,FHe said: "When I was five and started
OL,12,Fschool I was issued with a bike with
OL,13,Flittle wheels. It was a mile to
OL,14,Fschool, so I did two miles a day when
OL,15,FI was five and I've never stopped."
OL,17,FTony was introduced to Inspire Youth
OL,18,FZone by his granddaughter, Hannah.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777968371
OL,3,CMan, 91, to cycle over 500 miles to
OL,4,Craise money for youth zone
OL,6,FHe said: "They get hardly any
OL,7,Fgovernment money, it's all raised by
OL,8,Fpeople such as myself.
OL,10,F"For the youth of Chorley, I've got
OL,11,Fthis quote in my mind from our local
OL,12,FMP who said: 'It's the best thing
OL,13,Fthat's ever happened to Chorley,' and
OL,14,FI think that's very true."
OL,16,FTony said it's knowing the impact the
OL,17,Fyouth zone has on young people in
OL,18,FChorley is what inspires him to
OL,19,Fcomplete his challenges.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777968371
OL,3,CMan, 91, to cycle over 500 miles to
OL,4,Craise money for youth zone
OL,6,FHe said one boy stopped him in the
OL,7,Fstreet last year to tell Tony that he
OL,8,Fhad saved his life.
OL,10,FTony said: "What can you say to that?
OL,11,FThat convinced me about Inspire. He
OL,12,Fmeant my small contribution was
OL,13,Fkeeping Inspire going, and Inspire had
OL,14,Fturned his life around somewhere, and
OL,15,Fwe didn't go into detail.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777968371
OL,3,CMan, 91, to cycle over 500 miles to
OL,4,Craise money for youth zone
OL,6,F"But he won't be alone. There will be
OL,7,Falot of people in that place who get
OL,8,Fmind treatment as well as the physical
OL,9,Fstuff that keeps people happy on the
OL,10,Fsurface. But deeper down, the ones in
OL,11,Ftrouble are being helped, so we can't
OL,12,Flet it close."
OL,14,FTony's wife, Dorothy, who is 88,
OL,15,Fregularly cycles alongside him, and
OL,16,Fwill join him on the first leg of his
OL,17,Fchallenge.
OL,19,FShe said: "I'm very proud of him, he's
OL,20,Fvery good isn't he? I don't think
OL,21,Fanyone else would do this."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777968371
OL,3,CMan, 91, to cycle over 500 miles to
OL,4,Craise money for youth zone
OL,6,FHe has already raised #4,000 for this
OL,7,Fchallenge, with a goal of raising
OL,8,F#10,000 by the time he has finished.
OL,10,FTony's daughter, Ruth Gaspar, said:
OL,11,F"You just wonder how he can keep doing
OL,12,Fit because he's just ancient. I work
OL,13,Fin a dementia unit and you see people
OL,14,Fwho can't do these things so it's just
OL,15,Fwow.
OL,17,F"He's such an inspiration and his cup
OL,18,Fis always half full. He's just full of
OL,19,Flife and brilliant."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1777968371
OL,3,CMan, 91, to cycle over 500 miles to
OL,4,Craise money for youth zone
OL,6,FRuth and her husband Dennis will also
OL,7,Fjoin Tony for parts of the challenge,
OL,8,Fas well as his great grandsons, Moses
OL,9,Fand Beau.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/9
